Dragonfly/1 bat probe/Darkfate:

darkfate thought that he didn't left all work to Dragonfly and he 
send one of his probes to help him.

Dragonfly arrived where Angel Prime was, "I'm Dragonfly, I'm here 
instead my leader... he's busy... you know... Preds's troubles"

"Ruin this mission, bug, and I promise you that you'll regret it!!" 
Shouted Darkfate by Dragonfly commm link.

"Yes, sir" replied the bot and speaking with Angel Prime "He's mad... 
Guys like Hell Beast always make him up set"
